line_1: Thee Venice keeps, thee Genoa now regains;
line_2: And next the throne thy seat the Swede maintains;

line_1: His wounded Jaws; but whilst He thus Regains
line_2: His Liberty, the bearded wire remains

line_1: His wounded Jaws; but whilst He thus Regains
line_2: And galls his tender Gills with restless Pains.
